import React from 'react'

function Close(props: any) {
  return (
    <svg
      onClick={props.onClick}
      width="15"
      height="15"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    >
      <line
        x1="3"
        y1="21.2286"
        x2="20.5858"
        y2="3.64286"
        stroke="grey"
        strokeWidth="2"
        strokeLinecap="round"
      />
      <line
        x1="20.5863"
        y1="21"
        x2="3.00056"
        y2="3.41421"
        stroke="grey"
        strokeWidth="2"
        strokeLinecap="round"
      />
    </svg>
  )
}

export default Close
